com.commander4j.db

Class JDBQMSample

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.commander4j.db.JDBQMSample

  • public class JDBQMSample
extends java.lang.Object
    The JDBQMSample inserts rows into the APP_QM_SAMPLE table when Sample Labels are printed. Each sample is allocated a unique sample id. When results are entered into the database they are linked back to the original sample using this sample id.

    See Also:
    JDBQMInspection, JDBQMActivity, JDBQMDictionary, JDBQMTest
